Geant4 and JAIDA
    
    It is currently possible to use Geant4 with JAIDA <<3.2.x>>. The documentation on how to use the two
softwares together can be found on the {{{http://geant4.slac.stanford.edu/g4cd/Welcome.html}SLAC Geant4 Tutorial CD}}.

    Also refer to the documentation on how to use {{{cpp-jaida.html} JAIDA from C++}}.